::Shredder::

Shredder runs through the forest, Ramulus chasing after him. The ex-predacon 
had retreated when his scanners picked up two Maximals aproaching. He growls. 
The ram chasing him was pretty experienced, he had to give him that.

Several minutes later, Striker seemed to have lost the Maximal chasing him. 
He slows down slightly, heading for Magmatron's base.
